A User can see all Users he/she Follows in a list
A User can see all Communities he/she Follows in a list
A User can Follow a Community
A User can UnFollow a Community

A User can Follow another User
A User can UnFollow another User
Deleting a Community will trigger an UnFollow for all Users Following it
A User can Follow another User, even when he/she is Blocked by that User
A User receives a Notification if another User Follows him/her
A User Following another User sees posts Shared by that User on his/her Wall
If a User Follows a Community, all of that Community's Posts appear on that User's Wall
